tool_description: Get a real-time picture of economic indicators such as employment rates, consumer spending, mobility data, small business data, and COVID-19 health information.
name: COVID-19 Economic Impact
title: COVID-19 Economic Impact

api_list.name: United States COVID-19 Case Count
api_list.description: Get cumulative United States COVID-19 case count daily.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://covid-19-economic-impact.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/resources/covid-19-case-count-cumulative-us-daily"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "covid-19-economic-impact.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
